These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, cooking, video-games, camping
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, australian, mexican, russian
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, ship, subway, van
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person driving the van##1
2. the person driving the van is between the australian and the person who's hobby is singing##2
3. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
5. the argentine is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
6. the mexican is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
7. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | singing    | video-games      | cooking      | camping    |
| Nationality   | russian | argentine | australian | mexican |
| Transport     | ship    | van       | subway     | bus     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, october, april, november
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, photography, singing, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, romance, superhero, thriller
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
4. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
6. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
7. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |      4      |
| Birthday          | june     | november     | october       | april    |
| Hobby         | photography | singing   | card-games | woodworking |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller    | superhero | romance    | epic        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, fanta, soy-milk
There are 4 different nationalities: british, dutch, malaysian, polish
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, azure, apricot, pink
1. the dutch is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
3. the person who likes apricot is on the left or right of the british##3
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
5. the malaysian is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1
8. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | coffee  | fanta    | soy-milk |
| Nationality   | malaysian   | polish  | british  | dutch    |
| Color         | azure    | pink | orange | apricot  |

