.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-5::.
4 different games are played: whist, backgammon, domino, scrabble
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, dressmaker, lawyer, librarian
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, drama, romance, western
1. the person playing whist is on the far right##1
2. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
3. the lawyer is the person watching action movies##1
4. the architect is between the person playing domino and the person playing backgammon##2
5. the lawyer is on the right of the librarian##1
6. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
7. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
8. the person playing domino is the person watching romance movies##1
9. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Game          | domino      | scrabble | backgammon      | whist |
| Job           | dressmaker | architect | librarian | lawyer   |
| Movie-Genre   | romance    | western   | drama     | action   |

