.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, doctor, entrepreneur, videographer
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, baking, collecting, sudoku
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, biathlon, golf, rowing
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is the coach##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
3. the coach is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
6. the entrepreneur is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
7. the doctor is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
8. the doctor is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3       |      4       |
| Job           | coach    | doctor   | entrepreneur | videographer |
| Hobby   | board-games     | collecting   | sudoku         | baking        |
| Sport         | biathlon | baseball | golf         | rowing       |

