.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-12::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, mirinda, soy-milk, sprite
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, rowing, soccer, skiing
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, helicopter, skateboard, snowmobile
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
6. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person driving the helicopter and the person drinking mirinda##2
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's sport is rowing##1
8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |     2      |     3      |   4    |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate   | soy-milk   | mirinda    | sprite |
| Sport         | rowing | soccer    | swimming      | skiing |
| Transport   | helicopter      | snowmobile | skateboard | bike   |

