2. the fan of r&b is between the person drinking coffee and the fan of d&b##2
3. the fan of house is the person driving the train##1
4. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
5. the fan of house is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
6. the person drinking coffee is the fan of funk##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
8. the fan of funk is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
9. the person driving the snowmobile is the fan of d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | coffee      | almond-milk | milk       | iced-tea  |
| Music-Genre       | funk | r&b | d&b    | house |
| Transport   | scooter     | car         | snowmobile | train     |

