.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, collecting, drawing, photography
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, dancer, journalist, security-guard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, golf, skateboarding, surfing
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
2. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the bartender##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far right##1
8. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the journalist##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |    3     |       4        |
| Hobby    | drawing | collecting  | skydiving  | photography           |
| Job     | bartender | journalist | dancer   | security-guard |
| Sport   | surfing   | golf       | biathlon | skateboarding  |

 